page.title: 18TEBAY SCHOOL OPEN DAY
page.content: Pamela Murphy,Steven Murphy,lives at The Laurels Tebay & visited school in the afternoon to see Sara at work. Pamela Braithwaite lives at Bank Field,Tebay & came to school at 1400hrs to see Michael & others working.Doreen Newitt lives at:West view Old Tebay. Diane Snedker lives at north Tebay & came to visit Alison & Eleanor at school and so did Brenda Snedker.Marie Cowan lives at Bank View Tebay.Sheila Bradley lives at whinfell terrace Tebay & came to school to see Vicky at work.Brenda Snedker thought the children had all done very well. Jo Seward,lives in a cottage at Longdale,Tebay.I came to see Andrew's work.
